- [ ] **#2** Replace `<h1>loading</h1>` with a skeleton or deferred opacity-50 render
- [ ] **#3** Add column headers (Kategori, Butikk, Dato, Beløp, Bruker) — or `sr-only` equivalents
- [ ] **#4** Fix year text from `text-[0.6rem]` (9.6px) to minimum `text-xs` (12px)
- [ ] **#5** Replace hardcoded `bg-purple-950/10 text-purple-300` on category badge with semantic tokens
- [ ] **#5** Replace hardcoded `bg-pink-900` on user badge with semantic token
- [ ] **#6** Group filter controls visually with dividers between logical groups
- [ ] **#6** Remove `min-w-max` from QueryControls, add `overflow-x-auto` to its container
- [ ] **#6** Consider wrapping the filter bar in a card/muted background for separation
- [x] **#7** Move `{totalResults} rader` out of the search input addon into a table caption
- [ ] **#7** Expand to show `"Viser X av Y transaksjoner"` with pagination context
- [ ] **#8** Change ClearFiltersButton from `variant="destructive"` to `variant="ghost"` or `"outline"`
- [ ] **#8** Add a text label to the ClearFilters button (not icon-only)
- [ ] **#9** Replace `w-fit` on DataTable wrapper with `w-full`
- [ ] **#9** Add `max-w-screen-xl mx-auto` to the Dashboard container
- [ ] **#10** Move PageControls inside the DataTable footer, or wrap table + pagination in a shared Card
- [ ] **#11** Remove the stacked `User` icon from the user column cell — show badge only
